WEBVTT

00:01.401 --> 00:05.667
<i>Theorizing that one could time travel
within his own lifetime,</i>

00:05.739 --> 00:08.674
<i>Dr. Sam Beckett stepped
into the Quantum Leap accelerator...</i>

00:08.742 --> 00:10.733
<i>and vanished.</i>

00:16.015 --> 00:18.678
<i>He awoke to find himself
trapped in the past,</i>

00:18.752 --> 00:21.550
<i>facing mirror images
that were not his own...</i>

00:21.621 --> 00:26.854
<i>and driven by an unknown force
to change history for the better.</i>

00:26.926 --> 00:32.192
<i>His only guide on this journey is Al,
an observer from his own time,</i>

00:32.265 --> 00:36.634
<i>who appears in the form of a hologram
that only Sam can see and hear.</i>

00:36.703 --> 00:42.369
<i>And so, Dr. Beckett finds himself
leaping from life to life,</i>

00:42.442 --> 00:44.910
<i>striving to put right
what once went wrong...</i>

00:44.978 --> 00:47.503
<i>and hoping each time
that his next leap...</i>

00:47.580 --> 00:49.571
<i>will be the leap home.</i>

00:51.051 --> 00:53.815
<i>Come on, sister.!</i>

00:56.556 --> 01:00.822
We are here tonight not because
we want more rights than men have...

01:00.894 --> 01:05.991
<i>but because we want
the same rights men have.</i>

01:06.066 --> 01:09.126
I'm asking you to take a stand.

01:09.202 --> 01:13.104
<i>Show them that we are not gonna take
it anymore.! I'm asking you to burn it.</i>

01:13.173 --> 01:15.903
<i>Burn it for liberation now.!
Do it! Just do it!</i>

01:23.583 --> 01:26.677
<i>Liberation now.! Liberation now.!</i>

01:26.753 --> 01:29.187
Liberation now!
Oh, boy.

